targetInterventionId, T.TIMING AS timingId FROM T_CM_BASEBASE T LEFT OUTER JOIN T_TNFRREC transfer ON transfer.TRRC_ID = coalesce(T.case_tnfr, t.cmpr_tnfr) WHERE (coalesce(T.case_ownr, t.cmpr_ownr,
